text: Blabia bicuspis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Henry Walter Bates in 1866. It is known from Colombia, Brazil, Peru and Ecuador.BioLib.cz - Blabia bicuspis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Blabia Category:Beetles described in 1866
